{"tid":2401105,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰航空拖欠政府第一期優先股股息","createTime":"2021-02-09T12:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T02:58:05.000Z","uid":1086,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"64f535bf26465c3ba136e3db87ec56f45e3818b9","tid":2401105,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T12:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2875000/2875403/cxc_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2875000%2F2875403%2Fcxc_1024.jpeg&h=64c8a447&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國泰航空 （00293） 公布，董事局決定延遲派付原定於2021年2月16日到期應支付予優先股持有人的股息。國泰指，根據公司章程所載列的優先股條款規定，任何延遲派付的優先股股息將予累計並構成欠款，而在欠款完全支付前，國泰將不會派發普通股股息或回購其普通股。<br />\n<br />\n國泰去年6月獲政府注資，政府斥195億元認購國泰發行的優先股，而優先股的股息逐年遞增，首3年年利率為3厘、第4年為5厘、第5年為7厘，餘下年期則為9厘；股息按每半年支付一次。不過，條款亦訂明，國泰董事會可出於任何原因，選擇全部或部分推遲原定在股息支付日期應支付的股息。"},{"pid":"af4fadcba503a893fdbe322d3597dc3427c34e0e","tid":2401105,"uid":56618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T13:00:03.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">國泰董事會可出於任何原因，選擇全部或部分推遲原定在股息支付日期應支付的股息</span>"},{"pid":"386f158dbef173dc63ce935a6cf2bb1dacc8c7aa","tid":2401105,"uid":222907,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T13:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bQjsVJX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbQjsVJX.jpg&h=30c136d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7da0da832267bfa18dab81ac239c066339fe93f","tid":2401105,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T13:46:45.000Z","msg":"一早已經有人話撚咗佢實還唔到，呼吸plan嚟，3厘都無錢俾，去到之後9厘睇佢點還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0acf7d6257708efa7eae2e88f1ee9dbbdb73b7","tid":2401105,"uid":137038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy